Title: Localization techniques in quantum field theories
Authors: Vasily Pestun and Maxim Zabzine and Francesco Benini and Tudor Dimofte and Thomas T. Dumitrescu and Kazuo Hosomichi and Seok Kim and Kimyeong Lee and Bruno Le Floch and Marcos Marino and Joseph A. Minahan and David R. Morrison and Sara Pasquetti and Jian Qiu and Leonardo Rastelli and Shlomo S. Razamat and Silvu S. Pufu and Yuji Tachikawa and Brian Willett and Konstantin Zarembo
Abstract: This is the foreword to the special volume on localization techniques in quantum field theory. We summarize the individual chapters and their relation.
